article.description: — Chandler Leopard scored 21 points, all on 3-pointers, as Samford beat LaGrange 128-82 on Sunday night.
article.headline: Leonard buries 7 3-pointers and Samford earns 128-82 win against LaGrange
article.linkText: Leonard buries 7 3-pointers and Samford earns 128-82 win against LaGrange
article.story: BIRMINGHAM, Ala. -- — Chandler Leopard scored 21 points, all on 3-pointers, as Samford beat LaGrange 128-82 on Sunday night. Leopard finished 7 of 10 from 3-point range for the Bulldogs (7-2). Achor Achor scored 20 points while shooting 8 of 11 from the field and 4 for 6 from the line. Garrett Hicks added 14 points. The Bulldogs picked up their seventh straight victory. Camerin Lyons led the way for the Panthers with 12 points. Kameron McCall also scored 12 points for LaGrange. Gabe Cofield also had 10 points and three steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
